                    <h2 class="mt-4">Problem</h2>

                    <p>A1F needed a complete redesign of their website to alleviate some of the following issues:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The website was dated, difficult to update, and had many broken pages and features</li>
                        <li>Disorganized and duplicate information (multiple instances of polyhierarchy), unreadable content, and lack of mobile responsiveness</li>
                        <li>Low user engagement and conversion</li>
                        <li>Inability to capture basic user data was negatively affecting fundraising and research efforts</li>
                        <li>Was not easy for staff to update</li>
                    </ul>

