                    <ul>
                        <li>Improve modernity, general functionality and mobile responsiveness</li>
                        <li>Consolidate duplicate content, simplify information architecture, increase information discoverability</li>
                        <li>Increase donations and fundraising efforts</li>
                        <li>Increase genetic testing and awareness of AATD &mdash; target younger audience, possibly undiagnosed people starting families</li>
                        <li>Increase email newsletter signup conversion</li>
