                    <h2 class="mt-4">Information Architecture</h2>

                    <p>Based on the results of the card sort, we moved forward with:</p>

                    <ul class="">
                        <li>Main navigation with a simplified, logical topic-based category organization, eliminating all instances of polyhierarchy</li>
                        <li>Secondary "eyebrow" navigation for high-priority features/pages</li>
                        <li>Footer with some curated categories (Newly Diagnosed, Healthcare Providers, Resources)</li>
                        <li>Category sidebar navigation for content pages, instead of category overview/landing pages, to simplify site structure and enable quicker navigation</li>
                    </ul>
